Description: Provides real-time and historical access to financial data from
    African stock exchanges, including the Bourse Régionale des Valeurs
    Mobilières (BRVM) and other African markets. The package is designed to
    facilitate data retrieval, processing, and analysis for R users interested
    in African capital markets. It offers functions to query stock prices,
    trading volumes, market indices, and company-level information. Statistical
    tools for time-series analysis, normality testing, and exploratory data
    analysis are also included, making it suitable for both practitioners and
    researchers in African financial markets.
